query:
SELECT 
    controlname, 
    COUNT(*) AS nb_controls,
    SUM(rowsnumber) AS total_rows_generated,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN rowsnumber > 0 THEN 1 END) AS nb_controls_with_rows,
   round(100*COUNT(CASE WHEN rowsnumber > 0 THEN 1 END) / COUNT(*), 2) AS pct_controls_with_rows
FROM 
    admlogquery
 WHERE creationdate BETWEEN CAST(':startdate:' AS DATE) AND CAST(':enddate:' AS DATE) group by controlname
order by COUNT(*) desc
name: GTI - Control Summary
